<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.201478>
    dc:description "FIGURES 31 – 36. Ananteris palmari sp. nov., female holotype. 31 – 35. Distribution of the trichobothria (illustrated from right pedipalp). 31. Femur, dorsal aspect. 32. Patella, dorsal aspect. 33. Patella, external aspect. 34. Chela, dorsoexternal aspect. 35. Chela, ventral aspect. 36. Right chelicera, dorsal aspect. Scale bars equal 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/201478/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

